其他唔濕既野引發出來既臭</blockquote><br />\n我反而諗緊有咩唔濕嘅嘢會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講嘅唔濕係脫水 乾嘅嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"咸魚<br />\n甲醛"},{"pid":"ea959f67362e600978410ee829fadc639fc6a8b4","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T20:11:43.000Z","msg":"咸魚係咸香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53027cea77cbbfb0fd0c46567bd2aca945941ce","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T20:12:53.000Z","msg":"一陣風<br />\n一陣味<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一陣合理d"},{"pid":"1c8595f356c5d13fd999c920dede417cc946d81b","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53027cea77cbbfb0fd0c46567bd2aca945941ce","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T20:12:53.000Z","msg":"一陣風<br />\n一陣味<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一陣合理d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"其實係粵音嚟講<br />\n「陣」字通常用作量化時間<br />\n「一陣」、「等陣」、「陣間」<br />\n而用作量化「一堆」、「一團」嘅用法多數係書面語<br />\n「陣容」、「陣營」、「陣地」<br />\n如果純粹作日常溝通嘅話，係同「一祲」相通<br />\n至於想搵返讀音「浸」嘅本字<br />\n則「祲」較合理"},{"pid":"9aa1a9a5c6b26493112d53f1f06b1cf6b2ca613c","tid":613565,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"&quot;一浸&quot;解一層(eg &quot;面頭嗰浸&quot;)正字係咩?"},{"pid":"c8c3bc8b19d757f81dc65bee6f38d1956fbaa243","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;一浸&quot;解一層(eg &quot;面頭嗰浸&quot;)正字係咩?</blockquote><br />\n正字就係「浸」<br />\n【唐韻】【集韻】【正韻】子鴆切，音祲。漬也。<br />\n另外，【廣韻】七林切【集韻】千尋切，音侵。浸淫，漸漬也。<br />\n浸本身就可解作液體乾涸後，有殘餘物沉積係物件表面上"},{"pid":"9268c1023bf4a35fa4d70c6bc91ae83fe12b6a82","tid":613565,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8c3bc8b19d757f81dc65bee6f38d1956fbaa243","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;一浸&quot;解一層(eg &quot;面頭嗰浸&quot;)正字係咩?</blockquote><br />\n正字就係「浸」<br />\n【唐韻】【集韻】【正韻】子鴆切，音祲。漬也。<br />\n另外，【廣韻】七林切【集韻】千尋切，音侵。浸淫，漸漬也。<br />\n浸本身就可解作液體乾涸後，有殘餘物沉積係物件表面上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"唔知可以當量詞用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f3e868b33090c2b434d2df984c9441b0caa4ac","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&quot;一浸&quot;解一層(eg &quot;面頭嗰浸&quot;)正字係咩?</blockquote><br />\n正字就係「浸」<br />\n【唐韻】【集韻】【正韻】子鴆切，音祲。漬也。<br />\n另外，【廣韻】七林切【集韻】千尋切，音侵。浸淫，漸漬也。<br />\n浸本身就可解作液體乾涸後，有殘餘物沉積係物件表面上</blockquote>唔知可以當量詞用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然「浸」可在用作量詞用<br />\n而且所描述嘅事物同「祲」有相似性<br />\n兩者都可以分成「一層層」<br />\n但係「浸」只限於對液體表面一層凝固物嘅描述<br />\n「祲」就係用嚟代表不祥氣息，屬名詞<br />\n而「祲」本質上是否量詞亦無法考證"},{"pid":"12471123a1ee262e1255717786380983c6b0b72e","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb28a74bdb038a1e512bce38e22233efd90a7f8","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c8595f356c5d13fd999c920dede417cc946d81b","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53027cea77cbbfb0fd0c46567bd2aca945941ce","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T20:12:53.000Z","msg":"一陣風<br />\n一陣味<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一陣合理d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"其實係粵音嚟講<br />\n「陣」字通常用作量化時間<br />\n「一陣」、「等陣」、「陣間」<br />\n而用作量化「一堆」、「一團」嘅用法多數係書面語<br />\n「陣容」、「陣營」、「陣地」<br />\n如果純粹作日常溝通嘅話，係同「一祲」相通<br />\n至於想搵返讀音「浸」嘅本字<br />\n則「祲」較合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"陣風呢"},{"pid":"55b789a2c30004ad82504e8d61226713d6b53631","tid":613565,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"噴香水太濃都有人話臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189781a237c17dcbf4be1a5e5487be2777ae49a2","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb28a74bdb038a1e512bce38e22233efd90a7f8","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c8595f356c5d13fd999c920dede417cc946d81b","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53027cea77cbbfb0fd0c46567bd2aca945941ce","tid":613565,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T20:12:53.000Z","msg":"一陣風<br />\n一陣味<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一陣合理d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"其實係粵音嚟講<br />\n「陣」字通常用作量化時間<br />\n「一陣」、「等陣」、「陣間」<br />\n而用作量化「一堆」、「一團」嘅用法多數係書面語<br />\n「陣容」、「陣營」、「陣地」<br />\n如果純粹作日常溝通嘅話，係同「一祲」相通<br />\n至於想搵返讀音「浸」嘅本字<br />\n則「祲」較合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"陣風呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"無論係用作量詞用嘅「一陣風」定係名詞「陣風」<br />\n都係書面語"},{"pid":"b5739d353413117e990cdcffef1e19c8d8e9bd49","tid":613565,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}